BioCircos MFM Differential Expression Analysis

Deborah Velez-Irizarry

Thu Aug 29 10:04:45 EDT 2019

Transcriptomic and Proteomic Assesment of RER in Thoughbred Horses

Differential expression of genes and proteins identified in horses diagnosed with exertional rhabdomyolysis.

Transcription factor enrichment (TFE) analysis identified the heat shock transcription factor 4 (HSF4) enriched among the differentially expressed proteins. HSF4 was found to be differntially expressed in the transcriptome exhibiting a 1.7 fold change increase in horses with RER.
